The paper focuses on neural network-based models for machine comprehension and question answering, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of syntactic information and adaptation models, which are also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
